item.title: Personal Financial Tracker and Projector
item.description: I’ve been using an excel sheet to keep track of my finances and predict what they’ll look like for about a year and a half now. However, it doesn’t work in LibreOffice Calc, so I’ll have to make a program to mimic the behavior.
